IBM 's search engine combined results from ticket issuers and various providers in the ticket resale industry including ticket resale marketplaces such as RazorGator , StubHub , TicketNetwork and eBay , as well as ticket brokers including Ace Ticket , AllShows.com , Barry 's Tickets , Gold Coast Tickets and Las_Vegas_Tickets .

IBM 's search engine combined results from ticket issuers and various providers in the ticket resale industry including ticket resale marketplaces such as RazorGator , StubHub , TicketNetwork and eBay , as well as ticket brokers including Ace Ticket , AllShows.com , Barry 's Tickets , Gold Coast Tickets and Las Vegas Tickets .
IBM did not sell tickets directly to IBM end-users .

IBM was a state-owned record manufacturing company in Bulgaria founded in 1952 .
